midscene_run/output/
# run-history/ and midscene_run/report/ both stay ignored by default to
# keep the repo lean. For each case we force-add exactly ONE run JSON +
# ONE HTML report (the latest passing one) via `git add -f`. Local runs
# keep accumulating in these folders but stay out of git automatically.
# To refresh a case's tracked pair: `git rm` the old one and `git add -f`
# the new one.
